string stream is also used to break words
    string s;
    int t;
    cin>>t;
    cin.ignore()
    getline(cin,str)
    stringstream s(str); // Used for breaking words 
    string word; // to store individual words(string),u can alseo use integer also,int i;then s>>i
  
    int count = 0; 
    while (s >> word) 
        count++;
        cout<<word<<"\n";
        
Remember if you input no. test case or any integer then after using getline,you have to use *******************cin.ignore()************************** then use getline(cin,s)
